{"word":"ἐκνεύω","slug":"ἐκνεύω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>ἐκνεύω</b></el> <el>(<a href='S:future tense'>fut.</a> <el>σω</el>) (aor1 <el>ἐξένευσα</el>) </el><br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><a href='S:confer, compare'>cf.</a> <a href='S:ἐκνέω'><el>ἐκνέω</el></a>\n<p/><div class='li500'><b>I. </b><i>to turn the head aside</i>, <b><a href='S:Xenophon'>Xen.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>2. </b><a href='S:cum'>c.</a> <a href='S:accusative'>acc.</a> <i>to shun, avoid</i>, <b>Orph.</b><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>II. </b><i>to fall headlong</i>, <b><a href='S:Euripides'>Eur.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>III. </b><i>to give</i> one <i>a sign</i> to move away, <a href='S:cum'>c.</a> <a href='S:infinitive'>inf.</a>, <b><a href='S:Euripides'>Eur.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}